# Government Tender Announcement

**Title:** Request for Information (RFI) - 250 kW Low Frequency (LF) Broadcast System Replacement

**Reference Number:** WS4613651067-Document 4614089498

## Tender Details

* **Unicus Supply Class Code (USCC):** 52161523 - Radiator Frequency Transmitters or Receivers
* **Publication Date:** June 5, 2024
* **Tender Closes on:** July 31, 2024, at 2:00 PM EST
* **Procurement Category:** Goods and Services (GD)

## Request for Information

The Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC) on behalf of the Department of National Defense (DND) is seeking information from industry stakeholders regarding the replacement of the existing 250 kW LF Broadcast System. The Request for Information (RFI) is now closed, but the bid closing date has been extended for a period of time.
